originalText.text: I received my first facial ever with GBH Beauty, and have been going back ever since. The GBH team was able to help me maintain clear flawless skin, and also give me tips on maintaining healthy skin and a health beard. Heidy also recommended some amazing products to keep my skin looking great. My monthly facials have done wonders to how I feel, and been a boost to my self-confidence as a man. I can not wait for the pandemic to be over so I can resume monthly Facials.

originalText.text: I’ve been seeing Heidy for almost a year and my skin has done a total 180° change. I have acne prone skin and she has educated me on what I should do to property care for it and what to avoid. My skin has never looked better. She is friendly and looks out for her clients such as letting you know which ingredients are comedogenic and inflammatory which are key if you suffer from acne. I love when she has sales on her website and I take full advantage and stock up on Face Reality products! The location is super convenient for me because it’s accessible via bus or train.

originalText.text: Had a Brazilian wax done with her & it was amazing! It was almost completely painless — she was super patient with me yet very thorough. 10/10 would recommend!!
